14#ifndef ISC_TYPES_H
15#define ISC_TYPES_H 1
16
17#include <isc/bind9.h>
18
19/*! \file isc/types.h
20 * \brief
21 * OS-specific types, from the OS-specific include directories.
22 */
23#include <inttypes.h>
24#include <stdbool.h>
25#include <isc/offset.h>
26
27/*
28 * XXXDCL This is just for ISC_LIST and ISC_LINK, but gets all of the other
29 * list macros too.
30 */
31#include <isc/list.h>
32
33/* Core Types. Alphabetized by defined type. */
34
35typedef struct isc_appctx isc_appctx_t; /*%< Application context */
36typedef struct isc_backtrace_symmap isc_backtrace_symmap_t; /*%< Symbol Table Entry */
37typedef struct isc_buffer isc_buffer_t; /*%< Buffer */
38typedef ISC_LIST(isc_buffer_t) isc_bufferlist_t; /*%< Buffer List */
39typedef struct isc_constregion isc_constregion_t; /*%< Const region */
40typedef struct isc_consttextregion isc_consttextregion_t; /*%< Const Text Region */
41typedef struct isc_counter isc_counter_t; /*%< Counter */
42typedef int16_t isc_dscp_t; /*%< Diffserv code point */
43typedef struct isc_event isc_event_t; /*%< Event */
44typedef ISC_LIST(isc_event_t) isc_eventlist_t; /*%< Event List */
45typedef unsigned int isc_eventtype_t; /*%< Event Type */
46typedef uint32_t isc_fsaccess_t; /*%< FS Access */
47typedef struct isc_hash isc_hash_t; /*%< Hash */
48typedef struct isc_httpd isc_httpd_t; /*%< HTTP client */
49typedef void (isc_httpdfree_t)(isc_buffer_t *, void *); /*%< HTTP free function */
50typedef struct isc_httpdmgr isc_httpdmgr_t; /*%< HTTP manager */
51typedef struct isc_httpdurl isc_httpdurl_t; /*%< HTTP URL */
52typedef void (isc_httpdondestroy_t)(void *); /*%< Callback on destroying httpd */
53typedef struct isc_interface isc_interface_t; /*%< Interface */
54typedef struct isc_interfaceiter isc_interfaceiter_t; /*%< Interface Iterator */
55typedef struct isc_interval isc_interval_t; /*%< Interval */
56typedef struct isc_lex isc_lex_t; /*%< Lex */
57typedef struct isc_log isc_log_t; /*%< Log */
58typedef struct isc_logcategory isc_logcategory_t; /*%< Log Category */
59typedef struct isc_logconfig isc_logconfig_t; /*%< Log Configuration */
60typedef struct isc_logmodule isc_logmodule_t; /*%< Log Module */
61typedef struct isc_mem isc_mem_t; /*%< Memory */
62typedef struct isc_mempool isc_mempool_t; /*%< Memory Pool */
63typedef struct isc_netaddr isc_netaddr_t; /*%< Net Address */
64typedef struct isc_portset isc_portset_t; /*%< Port Set */
65typedef struct isc_quota isc_quota_t; /*%< Quota */
66typedef struct isc_ratelimiter isc_ratelimiter_t; /*%< Rate Limiter */
67typedef struct isc_region isc_region_t; /*%< Region */
68typedef uint64_t isc_resourcevalue_t; /*%< Resource Value */
69typedef unsigned int isc_result_t; /*%< Result */
70#ifndef ISC_PLATFORM_USE_NATIVE_RWLOCKS
71typedef struct isc_rwlock isc_rwlock_t; /*%< Read Write Lock */
72#else
73typedef pthread_rwlock_t isc_rwlock_t; /*%< Read Write Lock */
74#endif
75typedef struct isc_sockaddr isc_sockaddr_t; /*%< Socket Address */
76typedef ISC_LIST(isc_sockaddr_t) isc_sockaddrlist_t; /*%< Socket Address List */
77typedef struct isc_socket isc_socket_t; /*%< Socket */
78typedef struct isc_socketevent isc_socketevent_t; /*%< Socket Event */
79typedef struct isc_socketmgr isc_socketmgr_t; /*%< Socket Manager */
80typedef struct isc_stats isc_stats_t; /*%< Statistics */
81typedef int isc_statscounter_t; /*%< Statistics Counter */
82typedef struct isc_symtab isc_symtab_t; /*%< Symbol Table */
83typedef struct isc_task isc_task_t; /*%< Task */
84typedef ISC_LIST(isc_task_t) isc_tasklist_t; /*%< Task List */
85typedef struct isc_taskmgr isc_taskmgr_t; /*%< Task Manager */
86typedef struct isc_textregion isc_textregion_t; /*%< Text Region */
87typedef struct isc_time isc_time_t; /*%< Time */
88typedef struct isc_timer isc_timer_t; /*%< Timer */
89typedef struct isc_timermgr isc_timermgr_t; /*%< Timer Manager */
90
91typedef void (*isc_taskaction_t)(isc_task_t *, isc_event_t *);
92typedef int (*isc_sockfdwatch_t)(isc_task_t *, isc_socket_t *, void *, int);
93
94/* The following cannot be listed alphabetically due to forward reference */
95typedef isc_result_t (isc_httpdaction_t)(const char *url,
96 isc_httpdurl_t *urlinfo,
97 const char *querystring,
98 const char *headers,
99 void *arg,
100 unsigned int *retcode,
101 const char **retmsg,
102 const char **mimetype,
103 isc_buffer_t *body,
104 isc_httpdfree_t **freecb,
105 void **freecb_args);
106typedef bool (isc_httpdclientok_t)(const isc_sockaddr_t *, void *);
107
108/*% Resource */
109typedef enum {
110 isc_resource_coresize = 1,
111 isc_resource_cputime,
112 isc_resource_datasize,
113 isc_resource_filesize,
114 isc_resource_lockedmemory,
115 isc_resource_openfiles,
116 isc_resource_processes,
117 isc_resource_residentsize,
118 isc_resource_stacksize
119} isc_resource_t;
120
121/*% Statistics formats (text file or XML) */
122typedef enum {
123 isc_statsformat_file,
124 isc_statsformat_xml,
125 isc_statsformat_json
126} isc_statsformat_t;
127
128#endif /* ISC_TYPES_H */
